UNITED STATES v. HAM TOY et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 6, 1903.) No. 119. In Error to the District Court of the-United States for the Western District of New York. Chas. H. Brown, for plaintiff in error. Royal R. Scott, for defendant in error.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Judgment of District Court affirmed.
